-getRandomAds-latency-1749791449\n  RuleTriggerMethodAdapter.injectTriggerPoint : inserting trigger into hipstershop.AdService.getRandomAds() java.util.List\n  org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer : inserted trigger for AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749791449\n  ```\n\n### 下一步\n以下是处理建议：\n1. 检查 `AdService` 中的 Byteman 配置是否合理，避免多次注入。\n2. 确认 `AdService-getRandomAds` 方法在插桩后是否存在因性能埋点规则问题导致的运行延时异常。\n\n### 构造 JSON 输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"Agent failed to start!\",\n    \"java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException\",\n    \"Byteman agent\",\n    \"AdService-getRandomAds-latency\",\n    \"org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Byteman agent detected multiple injection attempts during initialization.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Caused by: java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Possible latency/stability issue due to Byteman rule insertion for AdService-getRandomAds.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer : inserted trigger for AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749791449\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
